		<li>c) payment organizations.</li>
	</ul>
</p>

<h3>How you can access and update your Personal information</h3>
<p>
	The accuracy of all information is important to Crampa. If any of the Personal Data provided changes, please advise us and
	we will update this. If you have questions over the Personal Data held, please ask us.
</p>

<h3>Legal rights relating to Personal Data</h3>
<p>
	Subject to the GDPR, the Individuals’ legal rights are:
