		<li>​a) the right of information;</li>
		<li>b) the right to rectification or cancellation;</li>
		<li>c) the right to restriction of processing;</li>
		<li>d) the right to data portability;</li>
		<li>e) the right to object to the processing of Personal Data.</li>
	</ul>

</p>

<p>
